Recommends: gstreamer1.0-vaapi
Description: Live wallpaper daemon and applet for COSMIC desktop
 Cosmic Flux renders GIF and video files as live wallpapers on the
 COSMIC desktop. It includes a Wayland layer-shell daemon (cosmic-flux-daemon)
 and a COSMIC panel applet (cosmic-applet-flux) for controlling playback,
 fit mode, FPS cap, and multi-monitor span mode.
